name: Atmosphere Regulators
desc: Industrial pumps, capable of storing, combining and releasing stored gasses deep within the planet.

name: Stellar Factory Relays
desc: Industrial factories and control centers, capable of producing stellar shades and mirrors that is launched into space.

name: Terrestrial Core Engines
desc: Underground mining facilities, capable of controlling tectonic and gravitational activity by manipulating the core of the planet.

name: Scientific Military Bases
desc: Research and subjugation facilities, capable of eliminating hostile forces and developing better surface conditions.
